Computer Modern TeX fonts (cm*.ttf) are bundled for Lasem math rendering.
They use the legacy TeX font encodings required for stretchy delimiters
(e.g. matrix brackets). Sourced from Matplotlib's font bundle (AMS/Bakoma).

Files:
  cmr10.ttf, cmmi10.ttf, cmsy10.ttf, cmex10.ttf